# =========================================
# VEDA Official Example 25
# Title: Action Library
# Concepts: action, do
# Difficulty: Intermediate
# =========================================

action welcome
    say: Welcome to VEDA!

action about
    say: VEDA is a simple programming language.

action help
    say: Learn. Build. Create.

action exit
    say: Thank you for using VEDA!

do welcome
do about
do help
do exit